+--
| ------------------------------------------------
| Key: A = Aqua   C = Clear  O = Orange B = Blue
|      Y = Yellow V = Violet R = Red    G = Green
|
| State            Color Transition Table
| ------------------------------------------------
|
| Here are a few examples which use solid colors:
|
| Idle             CCCCCCCCCCCCCCCC <-solid clear
| Sleeping         BBBBBBBBBBBBBBBB <-solid blue 
| Low CPU Usage    VVVVVVVVVVVVVVVV <-solid violet
| Mild CPU Usage   RRRRRRRRRRRRRRRR <-solid red
| Heavy CPU Usage  OOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO <-solid orange
| Severe CPU Usage YYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY <-solid yellow
| 
| Here are a few examples which use blinking:
|
| Attention        GGGGGGGGCCCCCCCC <-slow blink 
| Error            RRCCRRCCRRCCRRCC <-fast blink 
| Busy             ACCCACCCACCCACCC <-red flicker
| Insane           ROYGBVROYORVBGYO <-rainbow!
|
| ------------------------------------------------
+--
